{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1000,"text":"A human child is born,"},{"time":11000,"text":"and for quite a long time"},{"time":16000,"text":"is a consumer."},{"time":21000,"text":"It cannot be consciously a contributor."},{"time":33000,"text":"It is helpless."},{"time":35000,"text":"It doesn't know how to survive,"},{"time":38000,"text":"even though it is endowed with an instinct to survive."},{"time":53000,"text":"It needs the help of mother, or a foster mother, to survive."},{"time":69000,"text":"It can't afford to doubt the person who tends the child."},{"time":82000,"text":"It has to totally surrender,"},{"time":87000,"text":"as one surrenders to an anesthesiologist."}]},{"cues":[{"time":92000,"text":"It has to totally surrender."},{"time":98000,"text":"That implies a lot of trust."},{"time":108000,"text":"That implies the trusted person"},{"time":115000,"text":"won't violate the trust."},{"time":118000,"text":"As the child grows,"},{"time":123000,"text":"it begins to discover"},{"time":127000,"text":"that the person trusted is violating the trust."},{"time":133000,"text":"It doesn't know even the word \"violation.\""},{"time":138000,"text":"Therefore, it has to blame itself,"},{"time":144000,"text":"a wordless blame,"},{"time":147000,"text":"which is more difficult to really resolve --"},{"time":159000,"text":"the wordless self-blame."}]},{"cues":[{"time":165000,"text":"As the child grows to become an adult:"},{"time":170000,"text":"so far, it has been a consumer,"},{"time":174000,"text":"but the growth of a human being"},{"time":177000,"text":"lies in his or her capacity to contribute,"},{"time":187000,"text":"to be a contributor."},{"time":191000,"text":"One cannot contribute unless one feels secure,"},{"time":197000,"text":"one feels big,"},{"time":200000,"text":"one feels: I have enough."}]},{"cues":[{"time":206000,"text":"To be compassionate is not a joke."},{"time":210000,"text":"It's not that simple."},{"time":213000,"text":"One has to discover a certain bigness in oneself."},{"time":220000,"text":"That bigness should be centered on oneself,"},{"time":223000,"text":"not in terms of money,"},{"time":226000,"text":"not in terms of power you wield,"},{"time":230000,"text":"not in terms of any status that you can command in the society,"},{"time":238000,"text":"but it should be centered on oneself."},{"time":243000,"text":"The self: you are self-aware."},{"time":247000,"text":"On that self, it should be centered -- a bigness, a wholeness."},{"time":254000,"text":"Otherwise, compassion is just a word and a dream."}]},{"cues":[{"time":264000,"text":"You can be compassionate occasionally,"},{"time":269000,"text":"more moved by empathy"},{"time":273000,"text":"than by compassion."},{"time":280000,"text":"Thank God we are empathetic."},{"time":284000,"text":"When somebody's in pain, we pick up the pain."}]},{"cues":[{"time":289000,"text":"In a Wimbledon final match,"},{"time":296000,"text":"these two guys fight it out."},{"time":299000,"text":"Each one has got two games."},{"time":304000,"text":"It can be anybody's game."},{"time":307000,"text":"What they have sweated so far has no meaning."},{"time":314000,"text":"One person wins."},{"time":320000,"text":"The tennis etiquette is, both the players have to come to the net"},{"time":330000,"text":"and shake hands."},{"time":335000,"text":"The winner boxes the air"},{"time":338000,"text":"and kisses the ground,"},{"time":343000,"text":"throws his shirt as though somebody is waiting for it."},{"time":347000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":350000,"text":"And this guy has to come to the net."},{"time":354000,"text":"When he comes to the net,"},{"time":357000,"text":"you see, his whole face changes."},{"time":362000,"text":"It looks as though he's wishing that he didn't win."},{"time":367000,"text":"Why? Empathy."}]},{"cues":[{"time":372000,"text":"That's human heart."},{"time":374000,"text":"No human heart is denied of that empathy."},{"time":380000,"text":"No religion can demolish that by indoctrination."},{"time":386000,"text":"No culture, no nation and nationalism --"},{"time":392000,"text":"nothing can touch it"},{"time":395000,"text":"because it is empathy."},{"time":398000,"text":"And that capacity to empathize"},{"time":404000,"text":"is the window through which you reach out to people,"},{"time":412000,"text":"you do something that makes a difference in somebody's life --"},{"time":417000,"text":"even words, even time."}]},{"cues":[{"time":422000,"text":"Compassion is not defined in one form."},{"time":427000,"text":"There's no Indian compassion."},{"time":430000,"text":"There's no American compassion."},{"time":434000,"text":"It transcends nation, the gender, the age."},{"time":440000,"text":"Why? Because it is there in everybody."},{"time":451000,"text":"It's experienced by people occasionally."}]},{"cues":[{"time":458000,"text":"Then this occasional compassion,"},{"time":463000,"text":"we are not talking about --"},{"time":467000,"text":"it will never remain occasional."},{"time":470000,"text":"By mandate, you cannot make a person compassionate."},{"time":478000,"text":"You can't say, \"Please love me.\""},{"time":482000,"text":"Love is something you discover."},{"time":485000,"text":"It's not an action,"},{"time":490000,"text":"but in the English language, it is also an action."},{"time":495000,"text":"I will come to it later."}]},{"cues":[{"time":499000,"text":"So one has got to discover a certain wholeness."},{"time":506000,"text":"I am going to cite the possibility of being whole,"},{"time":513000,"text":"which is within our experience, everybody's experience."},{"time":520000,"text":"In spite of a very tragic life,"},{"time":529000,"text":"one is happy in moments which are very few and far between."},{"time":539000,"text":"And the one who is happy,"},{"time":542000,"text":"even for a slapstick joke,"},{"time":550000,"text":"accepts himself and also the scheme of things in which one finds oneself."}]},{"cues":[{"time":559000,"text":"That means the whole universe,"},{"time":563000,"text":"known things and unknown things."},{"time":567000,"text":"All of them are totally accepted"},{"time":573000,"text":"because you discover your wholeness in yourself."},{"time":579000,"text":"The subject -- \"me\" --"},{"time":583000,"text":"and the object -- the scheme of things --"},{"time":586000,"text":"fuse into oneness,"},{"time":591000,"text":"an experience nobody can say, \"I am denied of,\""},{"time":597000,"text":"an experience common to all and sundry."}]},{"cues":[{"time":603000,"text":"That experience confirms that, in spite of all your limitations --"},{"time":612000,"text":"all your wants, desires, unfulfilled, and the credit cards"},{"time":617000,"text":"and layoffs"},{"time":622000,"text":"and, finally, baldness --"},{"time":626000,"text":"you can be happy."},{"time":630000,"text":"But the extension of the logic is"},{"time":635000,"text":"that you don't need to fulfill your desire to be happy."},{"time":641000,"text":"You are the very happiness, the wholeness that you want to be."}]},{"cues":[{"time":647000,"text":"There's no choice in this:"},{"time":649000,"text":"that only confirms the reality"},{"time":655000,"text":"that the wholeness cannot be different from you,"},{"time":662000,"text":"cannot be minus you."},{"time":666000,"text":"It has got to be you."},{"time":669000,"text":"You cannot be a part of wholeness"},{"time":672000,"text":"and still be whole."},{"time":675000,"text":"Your moment of happiness reveals that reality,"},{"time":679000,"text":"that realization, that recognition:"},{"time":684000,"text":"\"Maybe I am the whole."},{"time":687000,"text":"Maybe the swami is right."}]},{"cues":[{"time":690000,"text":"Maybe the swami is right.\" You start your new life."},{"time":701000,"text":"Then everything becomes meaningful."},{"time":707000,"text":"I have no more reason to blame myself."},{"time":711000,"text":"If one has to blame oneself, one has a million reasons plus many."},{"time":717000,"text":"But if I say, in spite of my body being limited --"},{"time":723000,"text":"if it is black it is not white, if it is white it is not black:"},{"time":732000,"text":"body is limited any which way you look at it. Limited."}]},{"cues":[{"time":738000,"text":"Your knowledge is limited, health is limited,"},{"time":742000,"text":"and power is therefore limited,"},{"time":745000,"text":"and the cheerfulness is going to be limited."},{"time":750000,"text":"Compassion is going to be limited."},{"time":753000,"text":"Everything is going to be limitless."},{"time":758000,"text":"You cannot command compassion"},{"time":764000,"text":"unless you become limitless, and nobody can become limitless,"},{"time":768000,"text":"either you are or you are not. Period."},{"time":773000,"text":"And there is no way of your being not limitless too."}]},{"cues":[{"time":782000,"text":"Your own experience reveals, in spite of all limitations, you are the whole."},{"time":792000,"text":"And the wholeness is the reality of you"},{"time":797000,"text":"when you relate to the world."},{"time":799000,"text":"It is love first."},{"time":802000,"text":"When you relate to the world,"},{"time":804000,"text":"the dynamic manifestation of the wholeness"},{"time":809000,"text":"is, what we say, love."},{"time":814000,"text":"And itself becomes compassion"},{"time":818000,"text":"if the object that you relate to evokes that emotion."},{"time":829000,"text":"Then that again transforms into giving, into sharing."},{"time":839000,"text":"You express yourself because you have compassion."}]},{"cues":[{"time":845000,"text":"To discover compassion, you need to be compassionate."},{"time":851000,"text":"To discover the capacity to give and share,"},{"time":856000,"text":"you need to be giving and sharing."},{"time":858000,"text":"There is no shortcut: it is like swimming by swimming."},{"time":863000,"text":"You learn swimming by swimming."},{"time":867000,"text":"You cannot learn swimming on a foam mattress and enter into water."},{"time":871000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":873000,"text":"You learn swimming by swimming. You learn cycling by cycling."},{"time":877000,"text":"You learn cooking by cooking,"},{"time":879000,"text":"having some sympathetic people around you"},{"time":882000,"text":"to eat what you cook."},{"time":884000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":892000,"text":"And, therefore, what I say,"},{"time":896000,"text":"you have to fake it and make it."},{"time":898000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":905000,"text":"You need to."},{"time":908000,"text":"My predecessor meant that."},{"time":914000,"text":"You have to act it out."},{"time":919000,"text":"You have to act compassionately."}]},{"cues":[{"time":926000,"text":"There is no verb for compassion,"},{"time":931000,"text":"but you have an adverb for compassion."},{"time":935000,"text":"That's interesting to me."},{"time":939000,"text":"You act compassionately."},{"time":945000,"text":"But then, how to act compassionately if you don't have compassion?"},{"time":949000,"text":"That is where you fake."},{"time":952000,"text":"You fake it and make it. This is the mantra of the United States of America."},{"time":956000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":961000,"text":"You fake it and make it."},{"time":965000,"text":"You act compassionately as though you have compassion:"},{"time":968000,"text":"grind your teeth,"},{"time":971000,"text":"take all the support system."},{"time":973000,"text":"If you know how to pray, pray."},{"time":977000,"text":"Ask for compassion."},{"time":980000,"text":"Let me act compassionately."},{"time":983000,"text":"Do it."},{"time":985000,"text":"You'll discover compassion"},{"time":987000,"text":"and also slowly a relative compassion,"},{"time":992000,"text":"and slowly, perhaps if you get the right teaching,"},{"time":996000,"text":"you'll discover compassion is a dynamic manifestation"},{"time":1001000,"text":"of the reality of yourself, which is oneness, wholeness,"},{"time":1007000,"text":"and that's what you are."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1009000,"text":"With these words, thank you very much."},{"time":1012000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}